{
  "texts": [
    "The agent creates the VA system for analysis by task planning and execution, while the user uses the created VA system and refines agent outputs.",
    "R4 Multiple view composition:As new visualizations are added, older ones may become less relevant.",
    "To display the most recent results to the user, the visualization panel needs to be updated.",
    "However, it is crucial to avoid discarding previous results as they may be relevant to new insights.",
    "Users should be allowed to merge visualizations of interest even if they are not the latest."
  ]
}